import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import BreadCrumb from './BreadCrumb' import Catergory from './Catergory' import CollectionCatBar from './CollectionCatBar' import Navbar from './Navbar' const CollectionDetails = () => { const details = useSelector(state => state.collection.value) // console.log(details); const navigate = useNavigate(); const handleEnd = (e) => { navigate('/') } return (
Date : {details.date}
Total Loan : {details.totalLoan}
Bringing Amount : {details.bringAmount}
Total Amount: {details.totalIncome - details.totalLoan}
Total Income : {details.totalIncome}
) } export default CollectionDetails
